fit(25.10)                                                          fit(25.10)

Name
       fit - Fits the entire design in the viewable window

Syntax
       fit [-help]

       Fits the entire design in the viewable window. You can use this command
       at any stage of the design flow to view the design in entirety.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description of the fit command.

              For  a detailed description of the command, use the man command:
              man fit.

Related Information
              * zoomIn

              * zoomOut

              * View Menu chapter of the Menu Reference

                * Fit

